##How to let a new server join the exist HCI cluster
1. Insall the pve on the server &ndash;skip&mdash;
2. Let the new server join the pve cluster 1 2  #ssh login the server pvecm add 10.32.4.37   3. configure NTP server 1 2 3 4 5  cat &gt;&gt; /etc/systemd/timesyncd.conf &lt;&lt; EOF NTP=192.168.0.2 192.168.0.3 EOF # Restart systemd-timesyncd service to apply settings systemctl restart systemd-timesyncd   4.
